Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.53,0:21:23.34,Miring,Rika,0,0,0,,Aku membayangkan hal yang lebay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.85,0:21:28.85,Miring,Rika,0,0,0,,Tidak mungkin hidupku seperti dongeng dramatis.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.45,0:21:31.45,Miring,Rika,0,0,0,,Tetap tenanglah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.60,0:21:33.90,Utama,Nao,0,0,0,,Honjoji-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.90,0:21:35.18,Utama,Rika,0,0,0,,Iya?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.18,0:21:38.15,Utama,Nao,0,0,0,,Aku ingin jadi temanmu!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.00,0:21:43.17,Utama,Nao,0,0,0,,Tak lama lagi aku akan ke atelier bernama Katsushika.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.17,0:21:44.91,Utama,Nao,0,0,0,,Yaitu di Tokyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.30,0:21:47.70,Utama,Takuya,0,0,0,,Eh? Kau mau ke Tokyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.70,0:21:48.60,Utama,Nao,0,0,0,,Iya!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.60,0:21:49.56,Utama,Haruko/Izumi,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.56,0:21:51.25,Utama,Ikuko,0,0,0,,Kamu juga mau ke Tokyo, Nao-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.90,0:21:53.46,Utama,Nao,0,0,0,,Jadi, Honjoji-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.99,0:21:56.02,Utama,Nao,0,0,0,,Mohon bantuannya di sana!
